oces.","en":"And how many a city was insolent toward the command of its Lord and His messengers, so We took it to severe account and punished it with a terrible punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"وَكَأَيِّن","fr":"Et combien de","en":"And how many","tr":"waka-ayyin","isWaqf":false},{"position":2,"ar":"مِّن","fr":"de","en":"of","tr":"min","isWaqf":false},{"position":3,"ar":"قَرْيَةٍ","fr":"un cité","en":"a town","tr":"qaryatin","isWaqf":false},{"position":4,"ar":"عَتَتْ","fr":"se rebella","en":"rebelled","tr":"ʿatat","isWaqf":false},{"position":5,"ar":"عَنْ","fr":"contre","en":"against","tr":"ʿan","isWaqf":false},{"position":6,"ar":"أَمْرِ","fr":"(le) Ordre","en":"(the) Command","tr":"amri","isWaqf":false},{"position":7,"ar":"رَبِّهَا","fr":"(de) son Seigneur","en":"(of) its Lord","tr":"rabbihā","isWaqf":false},{"position":8,"ar":"وَرُسُلِهِۦ","fr":"et Ses Messagers","en":"and His Messengers","tr":"warusulihi","isWaqf":false},{"position":9,"ar":"فَحَاسَبْنَـٰهَا","fr":"donc Nous prit cela à compte","en":"so We took it to account","tr":"faḥāsabnāhā","isWaqf":false},{"position":10,"ar":"حِسَابًۭا","fr":"un compte","en":"an account","tr":"ḥisāban","isWaqf":false},{"position":11,"ar":"شَدِيدًۭا","fr":"sévère","en":"severe","tr":"shadīdan","isWaqf":false},{"position":12,"ar":"وَعَذَّبْنَـٰهَا","fr":"et Nous châtia cela","en":"and We punished it","tr":"waʿadhabnāhā","isWaqf":false},{"position":13,"ar":"عَذَابًۭا","fr":"un châtiment","en":"a punishment","tr":"ʿadhāban","isWaqf":false},{"position":14,"ar":"نُّكْرًۭا","fr":"terrible","en":"terrible","tr":"nuk'ran","isWaqf":false}]},{"ayah":9,"verseKey":"65:9","juz":28,"arabic":"فَذَاقَتْ وَبَالَ أَمْرِهَا وَكَانَ عَـٰقِبَةُ أَمْرِهَا خُسْرًا","fr":"Elles goûtèrent alors le péril dû à leur conduite, et leur sort fut la ruine.","en":"And it tasted the bad consequence of its affair [i.e., rebellion], and the outcome of its affair was loss.","words":[{"position":1,"ar":"فَذَاقَتْ","fr":"Donc cela goûta","en":"So it tasted"